abstract: >-
  Horosa for Windows v2.3.1 beta is a local-first metaphysics workstation that aligns the
  latest Mac-side work (a full astrocartography/ACG map upgrade with an analytic RA/Dec rewrite, landing-point/Local-Space/Parans analysis and theme-aware labels; new horary and electional auxiliary charts with Western judgment rule packs and event-chart save/restore; a Heluo Lishu completion; AI system-proxy support for Issue #9; the Liuren three-transmissions order fix and assorted UI fixes; plus the prior global day-boundary / late-zi-hour model, in-app auto-update, 数算 methods 邵子参评数 / 河洛理数, harmonic 调波 chart, Feng Shui React rewrite, AI connectivity/model-selection, Ollama-streaming, BaZi/Taiyi/PD, Qimen and clean-machine fixes) and AI Analysis rework, astrology modules, traditional Chinese methods,
  kentang/kin backend integrations, AI-assisted structured export, Python and Java
  services, and self-contained Windows desktop delivery into one cross-platform
  release line.

